    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="section">
                <head>Original Text</head>
                <div type="subsection">
                    <pb n="1" facs="#Birth_Certificate.jpg"/>
                    <head place="above">Official Extract</head>
                    <p> Released from <hi rend="italic underline" facs="#matareyaBureau">Al-Matareya
                            Health Bureau</hi>
                        <lb/>Name and place of residence of the applicant <hi
                            rend="italic underline">Sheikh Mohammed Al-Sayyid Al-Najdi</hi>
                        <space quantity="9" unit="chars"/>
                        <hi rend="italic underline">Al-Matareya</hi>
                        <lb/>The subject of which the extract is required <hi
                            rend="italic underline">Birth certificate of his son Ali</hi>
                        <lb/>Extracted from the book of <hi rend="italic underline">birth records of
                            Al-Matareya Health Bureau</hi>
                        <space quantity="9" unit="chars"/> In the year <hi rend="italic underline"
                            >1926</hi>
                        <space quantity="9" unit="chars"/> Page <hi rend="italic underline">75</hi>
                        <space quantity="9" unit="chars"/> Part <hi rend="italic underline"
                            >first</hi>
                        <lb/>Date of permission to give the extract__________ <space quantity="9"
                            unit="chars"/> In the year 192_ <space quantity="9" unit="chars"/>
                        Number__________ <space quantity="9" unit="chars"/> Of__________ <space
                            quantity="9" unit="chars"/>
                        <lb/>Collected fees <hi rend="italic underline">0120 Millime</hi> Warrant
                        number <hi rend="italic underline">114794</hi> On <hi
                            rend="italic underline">11th of April</hi> In the year <hi
                            rend="italic underline">1926</hi> Treasury of <hi
                            rend="italic underline">Al-Matareya Health Bureau</hi>
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div type="subsection">
                    <head place="above">The Requested Extract</head>
                    <p> Upon searching, it was found that the aforementioned records affirmatively
                        confirmed the presence on the date of the eighth of April of the year
                        one-thousand nine-hundred (900) <lb/>and twenty six (6) AD under the number
                        274 the name Ali with the name of the father being Mohammed Al-Sayyid
                        Al-Najdi <lb/>of a Muslim religion, Egyptian nationality, scientist as an occupation
                        and the name of the mother being Zainab Soliman <lb/>Al-Rayyes of a Muslim
                        religion, Egyptian nationality, none as an occupation dated <lb/>the eighth of
                        November in the year one-thousand nine-hundred (900) AD... <lb/>The newborn
                        was undocumented on birth, and executing upon a court ruling of the
                        courthouse in Esna to which the Esna Prosecution office 5051 <lb/>is
                        affiliated, first number April of the year 1926 on 483 </p>
                </div>
                <div type="subsection">
                    <head place="above">Footer</head>
                    <p> True copy <space quantity="9" unit="chars"/>Released on <hi
                            rend="italic underline">4/11</hi>In the year 192<hi
                            rend="italic underline">6</hi><space quantity="9" unit="chars"
                        />(Signature of the writer) <lb/>Handed over without the governmentâ€™s
                        responsibility whatsoever on what is included within and the rights of
                        others <lb/>(Signature of the pen heads)<space quantity="9" unit="chars"
                        />(Signature of the head of the department or the manager or the governor)
                        <lb/>Released on <hi rend="italic underline">the 17th of April</hi> in the
                        year 192<hi rend="italic underline">6</hi>
                        <lb/>Stamp of the body from which the extract was issued <lb/>(Amiri Press
                        6230/1920/15000) </p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div type="section">
                <head>Description and Breakdown</head>
                <div type="subsection">
